# Bug #001 — Login with invalid password fails

## Description
Entering an incorrect password causes the page to go blank instead of showing an error message.

## Steps to Reproduce
1. Open the login page
2. Enter email: test@example.com
3. Enter password: wrongpass123
4. Click "Login"

## Expected Result
Error message: "Invalid email or password" appears.

## Actual Result
Blank page.

## Status
Open

## Priority
High

# Bug #002 — Signup allows invalid email

## Description
Registration accepts an email without "@" symbol and creates an account.

## Steps
1. Open the signup page
2. Enter email: testexample.com
3. Enter password: 123456
4. Click "Submit"

## Expected Result
Error message: "Invalid email format"

## Actual Result
Account is created successfully

## Status
Open

## Priority
Medium

